    <lb n="11"/>ὑμῶν γείνεται. ἐγὼ μέντοι, δέσποτα, ἐ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ν</unclear> ῷ τέως ἐνταῦθα ἐπέχομαι πῆ μὲν διὰ τὰ 

    <lb n="12"/>ἔ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ργα</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" extent="4" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" extent="2" unit="character"/><subst><add place="inline">εβαλ<add place="supralinear">ό</add>μην</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">εβαλ<del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable"><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/></del>μην</del></subst> εἰς διαφορὰς <gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">κ</unclear><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ημ</unclear><gap reason="illegible" extent="4" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" extent="1" unit="character"/>ε<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">σι</unclear>ν <gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">κα</unclear>ὶ <gap reason="illegible" extent="4" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="4" unit="character"/> 

